            <title>[STORM-3302] Several HDFS sockets might leak</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-3302</link>
                <project id="12314820" key="STORM">Apache Storm</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have observed a nimbus instance with many socket connections open in &lt;tt&gt;CLOSE_WAIT&lt;/tt&gt; state. This indicates that we may have leaked socket connections.&lt;/p&gt;

